Class MasterImportImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MasterImport

    public class MasterImportImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements MasterImport
    An implementation of the model object 'Master Import'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Imported Master
    • Id
    • Credentials
    • Import Selector
